highlights.text: “八方來財(Stacks from All Sides)” by 攬佬SKAI ISYOURGOD has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 137 days straight.
Lý Hải Production has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Cho Con Được Ôm Ba (Original Soundtrack From "Lật Mặt 8: Vòng Tay Nắng") [feat. ChuChu]” is the highest at #10.
“một lời đồn” by Bệt Band is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #1.
“Shake It To The Max (FLY)” by MOLIY and Silent Addy is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 17 spots at #71.
